data.description: Welcome to this beautiful end-unit townhouse in the heart of Manassas, Virginia! This stunning 3-level Colonial Townhouse boasts an array of impressive features that will make you feel right at home.   With 4 spacious bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, there's plenty of room for the whole family to spread out and relax. The main level includes a formal living room and dining room, perfect for entertaining guests or hosting family gatherings.  Step outside to enjoy the serene fenced yard, complete with a deck and brick patio, ideal for soaking up the sun or enjoying a morning cup of coffee. The lush landscaping surrounding the property adds a touch of natural beauty to the outdoor space. Inside, the kitchen is a chef's dream with upgraded appliances and stunning granite countertops.   Whether this is your first purchase or looking to upgrade to a more spacious property, this townhouse is sure to impress. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your new home sweet home!
